MTKt_status MtkPathToProjParam ( int  path,
int  resolution_meters,
MTKt_MisrProjParam *  pp 
)

Get projection parameters.

Returns:
MTK_SUCCESS if successful.
Example:
In this example, we get the projection parameters for path 1 at 1100 meter resolution.
  MTKt_MisrProjParam pp = MTKT_MISRPROJPARAM_INIT;
  status = MtkPathToProjParam(1, 1100, &pp);
Parameters:
[in] path Path
[in] resolution_meters Resolution
[out] pp Projection Parameters
